  + [plan_state] is active
  + [planning_basis] is runtime now has conversation kernel, SOP protocol registry, proposal-derived SJS/DataDesign ledgers, and automatic run narrative updates
  + [current_readiness] is long_turn_ready_enough_for_bounded_work_with_Shaliach_runtime_as_next_gate
